These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, emerald, aquamarine, blood-red
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, spy, mystery, thriller
1. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##8
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
4. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
5. the person who likes blood-red is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
6. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes emerald##5
7. the person who likes emerald is somewhere between the person who likes coral and the person watching spy movies##7
8. the person who likes emerald and the person watching thriller movies have the same parity positions##9
9. the person who likes aquamarine and the person watching time-travel movies have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | coral | emerald | aquamarine     | blood-red |
| Pet           | mystery   | thriller     | spy | time-travel  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, january, may, november
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, taxi, roller, car
1. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the car and the person who's birthday is in january have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
4. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
5. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
6. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
7. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | november     | may    | june | january    |
| Hobby      | bus | taxi | roller      | car |

