.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, trike, bus, skateboard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, may, july, february
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
8. the person driving the trike and the person who's birthday is in may have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | trike    | bus   | car    | skateboard  |
| Food       | may | february | april | july |

