.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, lemon, pineapple, peach
4 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, turtle, pony
1. the owner of the dog is the person eating lemon##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
4. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
6. the person eating peach and the owner of the pony have the same parity positions##9
7. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | peach | pineapple | garlic  | lemon |
| Music-Genre   | turtle             | lizard          | pony | dog    |

