.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, banana, lemon, garlic
City: marseilles, hamburg, liverpool, edinburgh
1. the person eating lemon is not the person traveling to liverpool##6
2. the person traveling to marseilles and the person eating plum have different parity positions##9
3. the person traveling to hamburg and the person eating banana have different parity positions##9
4. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
6. the person eating banana is not the person traveling to hamburg##6
7. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person eating plum##1
9. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the person eating garlic##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | plum | lemon | garlic  | banana |
| Pet           | hamburg   | marseilles     | liverpool | edinburgh      |

