.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, pop, jazz, electronic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia, bellflower, balloon-flower
1. the fan pop is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan jazz is on the left of the fan electronic##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the left of the fan electronic##5
4. the person who growsmarigold and the fan jazz have the same parity positions##9
5. the fan electronic and the person who growsmarigold have different parity positions##9
6. the person who growsbellflower is not to the left of the fan punk##8
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the fan punk##5
8. the fan pop is not to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | pop | punk | jazz | electronic |
| Nationality   | balloon-flower        | bellflower    | marigold   | dahlia |

