3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the manager is on the left of the doctor##1
5. the doctor is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
6. the paramedic is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
7. the manager and the person who's birthday is in july have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | manager | doctor | scientist | paramedic |
| Pet     | april     | may     | july     | january    |

