2. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the fisherman##8
3. the person watching epic movies is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
4. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
5. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the electrician##3
6. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
7. the fisherman is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
8. the person watching horror movies is the software-developer##1
9. the person watching animation movies and the fisherman have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | thriller   | animation    | epic | horror    |
| Nationality   | entrepreneur | fisherman | electrician   | software-developer |

