.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, pear, tomato, asparagus
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, april, january
 1. the person eating pear and the person who's birthday is in april have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person eating tomato is not to the right of the person eating pear##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person eating pear and the person eating carrot##7
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
 5. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the left of the person eating asparagus##8
 7. the person eating asparagus and the person who's birthday is in october have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | carrot  | asparagus | tomato  | pear |
| Music-Genre   | january | april     | june | october     |

