.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, february, may, october
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, cycling, rugby, basketball
1. the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's sport is golf have the same parity positions##9
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person who's sport is golf##8
4. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
5. the person who's sport is golf is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's birthday is in april have the same parity positions##9
7. the person who's sport is golf and the person who's birthday is in may have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | april | october | february | may |
| Pet   | rugby    | cycling   | basketball        | golf            |

