.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, june, october, july
House: tower, gothic-revival, palace, farmhouse
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the tower house##1
 2. the palace house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the farmhouse house is not to the right of the palace house##8
 4. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
 5. the tower house is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in july and the gothic-revival house have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is the gothic-revival house##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june and the gothic-revival house have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | june    | october        | july   | may      |
| Hobby      | farmhouse | palace | gothic-revival | tower |

 